    <h2><a href="articles/vibe-coding-is-kinda-like-drunk-coding">Vibe coding is kinda like drunk coding</a></h2>
    <div class="variables">
    <div class="date">@date=2026-01-25</div>
    <div class="tags">@tags=<a href="tags/gamedev">gamedev</a>, <a href="tags/jewel-defender">jewel-defender</a></div>
